  "informal_statement": "For a real number r and natural n, the finite geometric sum 1 + r + ... + r^(n-1) times (r - 1) equals r^n - 1.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "The telescoping identity for finite geometric series: `geom_sum_mul`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem geom_series_mul (r : ℝ) (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range n, r ^ i) * (r - 1) = r ^ n - 1",
